1
00:00:00,005 --> 00:00:42,005
(Watch on www.kisskh.li Support Admin)

2
00:00:42,689 --> 00:00:43,715
[This drama is a work of fiction.]

3
00:00:43,715 --> 00:00:44,747
[Any resemblance to real persons,
places, or events is coincidental.]

4
00:00:44,747 --> 00:00:45,764
[Scenes with child actors and animals
were filmed safely]

5
00:00:45,764 --> 00:00:47,569
[under professional supervision.]

6
00:00:47,569 --> 00:00:49,862
We should bury the recording.

7
00:00:49,862 --> 00:00:51,789
Yeah.

8
00:00:53,814 --> 00:00:57,702
We're killing this project here.

9
00:00:57,702 --> 00:01:00,999
Pull everything tied to
Park Jae Sang and Oh Kwang Jae.

10
00:01:00,999 --> 00:01:03,126
And shelve the recording release.

11
00:01:03,126 --> 00:01:04,182
Understood.

12
00:01:04,182 --> 00:01:08,042
With the chairman involved,
it's too risky to keep pushing.

13
00:01:08,042 --> 00:01:10,926
I'll reach out to Park Jae Sang
and put the project on hold.

14
00:01:10,926 --> 00:01:12,803
And

15
00:01:12,803 --> 00:01:15,142
bring me a Plan B.

16
00:01:15,142 --> 00:01:16,981
Got it.

17
00:01:18,064 --> 00:01:20,772
The number you have dialed is not available.

18
00:01:20,772 --> 00:01:23,696
Why isn't he picking up?

19
00:01:27,564 --> 00:01:29,368
Leech.

20
00:01:30,939 --> 00:01:32,364
What the...

21
00:01:32,364 --> 00:01:35,082
[Episode 6]

22
00:01:37,119 --> 00:01:39,064
Hey!

23
00:01:39,064 --> 00:01:41,964
I said I'm not doing it.

24
00:01:45,752 --> 00:01:48,046
I'm through with all the expose crap.

25
00:01:48,046 --> 00:01:50,344
I told you, it's over!

26
00:01:50,344 --> 00:01:52,975
There's really no copy left?

27
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:55,805
Park Jae Sang's the one who has it.

28
00:01:55,805 --> 00:01:58,564
How many times must I repeat myself?
It's not with me!

29
00:01:58,564 --> 00:02:01,464
Looks like there's nothing here.

30
00:02:01,464 --> 00:02:04,772
I ran the IP and combed every server.

31
00:02:04,772 --> 00:02:08,115
Nothing's surviving on the web either.

32
00:02:23,751 --> 00:02:25,424
What are you doing?

33
00:02:27,897 --> 00:02:29,563
What?

34
00:02:29,563 --> 00:02:31,639
I said, what are you doing?

35
00:02:33,981 --> 00:02:35,647
That's gasoline?

36
00:02:35,647 --> 00:02:38,978
Are you insane? What the fuck is this?

37
00:02:40,897 --> 00:02:44,769
Look, I'll...

38
00:02:44,769 --> 00:02:46,396
I'll convince Director Lee myself, okay?

39
00:02:46,396 --> 00:02:48,664
Enough of this.

40
00:02:48,664 --> 00:02:52,212
Even if you all pull the broadcast,

41
00:02:52,212 --> 00:02:54,870
Park Jae Sang isn't backing down.

42
00:03:11,738 --> 00:03:14,348
Where are you hiding Park Jae Sang?

43
00:03:27,471 --> 00:03:29,063
Just one hour, please.

44
00:03:29,063 --> 00:03:31,115
Yes, understood.

45
00:04:00,059 --> 00:04:02,438
Jae Sang.

46
00:04:02,438 --> 00:04:04,690
I'm so sorry.

47
00:04:09,846 --> 00:04:12,480
What would it take

48
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:15,047
for you to let this go?

49
00:04:15,047 --> 00:04:16,869
You want forgiveness?

50
00:04:18,507 --> 00:04:22,124
I want to see you destroyed, too.

51
00:04:23,576 --> 00:04:26,086
To be stabbed in the back the same way...

52
00:04:27,822 --> 00:04:30,174
and to experience the same pain I went through.

53
00:04:37,689 --> 00:04:40,517
I've been suffering, too.

54
00:04:41,330 --> 00:04:45,230
I was desperate and blurted it out.

55
00:04:50,230 --> 00:04:53,322
I never thought it would...

56
00:04:55,563 --> 00:04:57,910
actually happen.

57
00:05:09,433 --> 00:05:11,590
Please forgive me.

58
00:05:25,138 --> 00:05:27,690
So, Jae Sang...

59
00:05:29,263 --> 00:05:31,276
The recording...

60
00:05:33,563 --> 00:05:36,448
can't you just bury it?

61
00:05:49,579 --> 00:05:52,462
This was about the recording?

62
00:05:52,462 --> 00:05:55,342
My whole life fell apart,

63
00:05:56,435 --> 00:05:59,555
and all you care about is your image?

64
00:06:05,756 --> 00:06:07,771
Then deal with it.

65
00:06:09,055 --> 00:06:11,483
That's exactly what I'm after.

66
00:06:35,098 --> 00:06:37,676
Talking to you is pointless now.

67
00:06:42,563 --> 00:06:44,767
I'm done trying.

68
00:06:47,438 --> 00:06:48,468
What?

69
00:06:48,468 --> 00:06:51,482
I'm sick of pretending around you.

70
00:07:06,072 --> 00:07:09,249
So you're pushing this to the end?

71
00:07:12,063 --> 00:07:14,463
Alright. Bring it on.

72
00:07:17,647 --> 00:07:18,782
Hey.

73
00:07:18,782 --> 00:07:20,969
Please don't say

74
00:07:21,853 --> 00:07:24,932
you believed we had a future?

75
00:07:27,468 --> 00:07:30,187
You pictured us walking down the aisle?

76
00:07:31,188 --> 00:07:33,941
What a complete idiot.

77
00:07:40,689 --> 00:07:45,035
Just die. Just die!

78
00:07:45,647 --> 00:07:47,913
That's Chu Sang Ah, right?

79
00:07:51,313 --> 00:07:54,227
He's going to kill her at this rate.

80
00:07:54,227 --> 00:07:56,105
What's he doing?

81
00:07:56,105 --> 00:07:58,799
Somebody needs to call the police.

82
00:08:00,168 --> 00:08:01,188
He's lost his mind.

83
00:08:01,188 --> 00:08:03,629
- Isn't he killing her?
- Somebody has to step in.

84
00:08:03,629 --> 00:08:06,466
- She'll be dead if this keeps up!
- Please, someone call for help!

85
00:08:06,466 --> 00:08:08,701
Somebody help!

86
00:08:10,647 --> 00:08:12,717
Hey, Park Jae Sang!

87
00:08:14,373 --> 00:08:16,957
Let go of her! I said let go!

88
00:08:18,770 --> 00:08:21,355
Don't come closer!

89
00:08:21,355 --> 00:08:22,691
Is that a knife he's got?

90
00:08:22,691 --> 00:08:23,733
What's going on?

91
00:08:23,733 --> 00:08:26,159
- Someone call the cops.
- Out of my way!

92
00:08:26,159 --> 00:08:28,480
Get out of the way!

93
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:30,873
Shouldn't somebody grab him?

94
00:08:32,605 --> 00:08:33,987
You alright?

95
00:08:33,987 --> 00:08:35,878
Put the cameras down!

96
00:08:36,468 --> 00:08:38,505
I told you, quit recording!

97
00:08:41,939 --> 00:08:44,478
Just record it.

98
00:08:44,478 --> 00:08:45,505
Oh no.

99
00:08:45,505 --> 00:08:46,772
Is he just trying to scare her?

100
00:08:46,772 --> 00:08:47,772
What if she ends up dead?

101
00:08:47,772 --> 00:08:48,814
What's going on?

102
00:08:48,814 --> 00:08:51,260
- We should report this.
- Who is that?

103
00:08:51,260 --> 00:08:54,066
[Sang Ah]

104
00:08:55,772 --> 00:08:57,153
The call could not be connected

105
00:08:57,153 --> 00:08:59,477
and was forwarded to voicemail.

106
00:08:59,477 --> 00:09:01,438
Record your message after the beep.

107
00:09:01,438 --> 00:09:04,615
Hang up when you're finished.

108
00:09:27,752 --> 00:09:29,572
You met with Choi Ji Ho, right?

109
00:09:29,572 --> 00:09:31,512
Find anything else?

110
00:09:31,512 --> 00:09:34,452
Choi Ji Ho doesn't have any copies.

111
00:09:34,452 --> 00:09:37,390
The recording leak's been called off.

112
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:40,612
All that's left is Park Jae Sang.

113
00:09:40,612 --> 00:09:42,092
Where the hell is he?

114
00:09:42,092 --> 00:09:44,146
We've narrowed it to the motel area.

115
00:09:44,146 --> 00:09:46,865
I'll send the pinpoint once it's locked.

116
00:09:52,411 --> 00:09:55,624
Sang Ah's been unreachable since yesterday.

117
00:09:58,178 --> 00:10:00,170
Do you know anything?

118
00:10:02,374 --> 00:10:04,526
I'll look into it.

119
00:10:05,305 --> 00:10:07,260
Last night...

120
00:10:12,397 --> 00:10:14,768
Sang Ah was with you, wasn't she?

121
00:10:21,177 --> 00:10:23,352
You're supposed to observe and report.

122
00:10:23,352 --> 00:10:26,606
But last night, you went too far.

123
00:10:26,606 --> 00:10:28,907
Why pull something like that now?

124
00:10:35,355 --> 00:10:37,666
You're the one who pushed me to this.

125
00:10:45,958 --> 00:10:49,177
Were you listening in on us last night?

126
00:10:50,446 --> 00:10:54,599
I sent you after Park Jae Sang,
not to spy on me!

127
00:10:57,094 --> 00:11:00,848
What's got you this shaken up?

128
00:11:00,848 --> 00:11:03,059
I mean, of course.

129
00:11:03,059 --> 00:11:05,605
You let your precious wife

130
00:11:05,605 --> 00:11:08,189
carry a murder on her back. And now it's out.

131
00:11:08,189 --> 00:11:10,431
- Scared, right?
- I warned you, know your place.

132
00:11:10,431 --> 00:11:13,577
You've been using Sang Ah all along.

133
00:11:15,750 --> 00:11:17,511
Hey.

134
00:11:19,451 --> 00:11:21,311
You caught a bit of our talk,

135
00:11:21,311 --> 00:11:24,210
and now you're flapping your lips.

136
00:11:24,210 --> 00:11:26,541
My patience for taking you in

137
00:11:26,541 --> 00:11:28,842
and looking after you has its limits.

138
00:11:33,387 --> 00:11:36,516
Isn't it me you really need right now?

139
00:11:47,405 --> 00:11:49,821
Want me to kill him?

140
00:11:51,397 --> 00:11:53,325
Park Jae Sang.

141
00:12:05,413 --> 00:12:07,631
We're done here.

142
00:12:09,043 --> 00:12:13,095
Stay away from me and Sang Ah for good.

143
00:12:29,981 --> 00:12:33,115
Piece of shit.

144
00:13:22,922 --> 00:13:25,442
Made up your mind, Chairman?

145
00:13:25,442 --> 00:13:28,670
I'm going to stoke the fire.

146
00:13:33,479 --> 00:13:35,427
Executive Director Kwon?

147
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:40,348
Quick on the uptake, as usual.

148
00:13:41,608 --> 00:13:43,727
Mr. Bang.

149
00:13:44,438 --> 00:13:46,782
Thank you.

150
00:13:46,782 --> 00:13:48,939
For what?

151
00:13:48,939 --> 00:13:50,942
Just thank you.

152
00:13:52,188 --> 00:13:54,779
Thank you.

153
00:13:57,358 --> 00:14:00,118
What exactly did you pull

154
00:14:01,045 --> 00:14:03,522
for the old man to collapse

155
00:14:03,522 --> 00:14:05,790
right after you walked out?

156
00:14:09,188 --> 00:14:10,788
The way the will reads now,

157
00:14:10,788 --> 00:14:14,591
WR lands in my hands on its own.

158
00:14:17,855 --> 00:14:19,930
Tough break, huh?

159
00:14:20,855 --> 00:14:23,975
I don't need you anymore.

160
00:14:27,098 --> 00:14:28,918
So you're telling me,

161
00:14:28,918 --> 00:14:30,976
with the will as it stands,

162
00:14:30,976 --> 00:14:33,078
I might come out on the losing end?

163
00:14:33,078 --> 00:14:36,355
[Leaking WR Group info means]
According to the Chairman's revisions,

164
00:14:36,355 --> 00:14:39,817
should WR's secrets get out
and tarnish the Group,

165
00:14:39,817 --> 00:14:41,772
[losing all rights and shares, instantly]
every right and share of that heir

166
00:14:41,772 --> 00:14:43,658
will be stripped away.

167
00:14:43,658 --> 00:14:46,623
You'd better kill that story immediately.

168
00:14:49,272 --> 00:14:51,512
And that's precisely

169
00:14:51,512 --> 00:14:55,924
why I'll be adding gasoline to your fire.

170
00:14:59,903 --> 00:15:02,764
What the hell is he doing?

171
00:15:03,897 --> 00:15:05,676
Because that's become...

172
00:15:05,676 --> 00:15:09,604
my way of protecting my shares.

173
00:15:13,438 --> 00:15:15,402
Mr. Kwon.

174
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:20,156
If that's how you play it, I'll go all in.

175
00:15:21,563 --> 00:15:24,661
If something tarnishes Chairman Kwon's name,

176
00:15:25,355 --> 00:15:27,998
you're fine with that?

177
00:15:38,614 --> 00:15:40,802
My father beat me

178
00:15:43,088 --> 00:15:47,438
every day until I turned twenty.

179
00:15:47,438 --> 00:15:48,897
The Group's honor, who cares.

180
00:15:48,897 --> 00:15:52,230
I'll make up scandals just to expose them.

181
00:15:56,359 --> 00:15:57,729
So...

182
00:15:57,729 --> 00:16:00,989
I'll set the whole thing ablaze.

183
00:16:03,814 --> 00:16:06,036
Just watch.

184
00:16:25,799 --> 00:16:27,230
You think the card I'm holding

185
00:16:27,230 --> 00:16:31,186
just brings down the Chairman alone?

186
00:16:32,605 --> 00:16:34,481
What card?

187
00:16:37,397 --> 00:16:39,694
The Oh Kwang Jae file.

188
00:16:40,397 --> 00:16:41,939
Press,

189
00:16:41,939 --> 00:16:45,588
cabinet members, moguls, all tied in.

190
00:16:45,588 --> 00:16:50,078
If that file comes out, can you survive it?

191
00:16:50,078 --> 00:16:52,908
The moment my wife speaks publicly,

192
00:16:52,908 --> 00:16:56,695
my name will be cleared.

193
00:16:56,695 --> 00:16:59,638
The grounds are more than sufficient.

194
00:16:59,638 --> 00:17:02,522
Get me that nomination as promised.

195
00:17:02,522 --> 00:17:04,629
But...

196
00:17:04,629 --> 00:17:08,139
what's the point of surviving on your own?

197
00:17:09,397 --> 00:17:12,775
When Chu Sang Ah falls, you fall with her.

198
00:17:12,775 --> 00:17:16,022
You're both tied to the same rope, right?

199
00:17:18,350 --> 00:17:22,238
Looks like a Doberman needs putting down.

200
00:18:17,155 --> 00:18:19,230
The Changjo Party has revealed

201
00:18:19,230 --> 00:18:22,034
it's weighing the withdrawal
of Bang Tae Seop's bid.

202
00:18:22,034 --> 00:18:27,669
[Changjo Party Holds Urgent Nomination Review]
We're reviewing his nomination status.

203
00:18:27,669 --> 00:18:31,076
As moral standards are the priority,

204
00:18:31,076 --> 00:18:33,342
we'll establish the facts
and deliver our stance shortly.

205
00:18:33,342 --> 00:18:35,399
[Prosecutors Mull Calling In Bang Tae Seop]
Looks like the prosecution's reopening

206
00:18:35,399 --> 00:18:37,581
the Oh Kwang Jae case.

207
00:18:37,581 --> 00:18:40,391
[Citizens Urge Revival of Oh Kwang Jae Case]
The ruling should come in a few days,

208
00:18:40,391 --> 00:18:42,602
[Chu Sang Ah, Murderer]
and whether Park Jae Sang's recording

209
00:18:42,602 --> 00:18:45,437
[Hold Bang Tae Seop Accountable for His Lies]
is released will be the key element.

210
00:18:45,437 --> 00:18:46,585
[Look Into All Parties Connected!]

211
00:18:46,585 --> 00:18:47,564
We have breaking news.

212
00:18:47,564 --> 00:18:50,734
[25,345 Demand the Case Be Reopened]
Chu Sang Ah was assaulted by Park Jae Sang

213
00:18:50,734 --> 00:18:52,480
[Conduct a Thorough Probe for the Truth]
in Deokyang-dong earlier today,

214
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:54,355
[Prosecution Must Revisit This Case Now]
and the clip is circulating on the web.

215
00:18:54,355 --> 00:18:57,199
[Citizen Footage, Park Jae Sang's Rampage]
Park is seen strangling Sang Ah on video

216
00:18:57,199 --> 00:18:59,159
[Ex-Convict Park Menaces Sang Ah and Escapes]
and waving a blade at her manager.

217
00:18:59,159 --> 00:19:02,162
The violent attack was captured on film.

218
00:19:02,162 --> 00:19:04,123
[Sang Ah's Life Not in Danger, Sources Say]
Authorities are reviewing CCTV footage

219
00:19:04,123 --> 00:19:07,003
[Authorities Hunt Park Jae Sang Using CCTV]
to locate the suspect on the run.

220
00:19:07,003 --> 00:19:09,169
[Murderer: Chu Sang Ah]
Once the footage came out, some sympathy

221
00:19:09,169 --> 00:19:10,897
[Quit the show. We see through the setup]
for Chu Sang Ah did surface,

222
00:19:10,897 --> 00:19:13,924
[She deserved it. Should've gone harder]
but the general online reaction was brutal.

223
00:19:13,924 --> 00:19:17,678
[Drop dead, Sang Ah! Maybe then we'll forgive]
The studios and sponsors who hired her

224
00:19:17,678 --> 00:19:22,357
are gearing up for massive penalty suits.

225
00:19:40,117 --> 00:19:41,820
[The Truth Behind the Oh Kwang Jae Murder]

226
00:19:44,039 --> 00:19:47,966
I can't pull back from this any longer.

227
00:19:48,781 --> 00:19:51,469
This evening at 8:30,

228
00:19:52,522 --> 00:19:53,922
I'm going to expose

229
00:19:53,922 --> 00:19:58,886
Sang Ah's actual voice
recorded seven years ago,

230
00:19:58,886 --> 00:20:02,515
to everyone linked to Oh Kwang Jae's death.

231
00:20:02,515 --> 00:20:04,774
I'm laying it all bare.

232
00:20:05,392 --> 00:20:07,062
[Sang Ah]

233
00:20:07,062 --> 00:20:09,822
[Live broadcast launches at 20:30]

234
00:20:12,317 --> 00:20:14,014
Where are you?

235
00:20:14,014 --> 00:20:15,785
You saw that?

236
00:20:16,647 --> 00:20:18,997
I'll take care of it,

237
00:20:19,939 --> 00:20:21,094
so...

238
00:20:21,094 --> 00:20:23,034
No...

239
00:20:23,034 --> 00:20:25,878
This is our punishment right now.

240
00:20:28,014 --> 00:20:31,134
You told me this when you proposed.

241
00:20:32,354 --> 00:20:34,846
That we're the same kind of people,

242
00:20:35,438 --> 00:20:37,807
that we can't do without each other.

243
00:20:39,772 --> 00:20:41,561
Right.

244
00:20:43,014 --> 00:20:46,038
We really are the same kind.

245
00:20:46,038 --> 00:20:48,026
A pair of hypocrites.

246
00:20:48,727 --> 00:20:51,105
- Sang Ah, listen...
- Vowing to avenge Han Ji Soo,

247
00:20:51,105 --> 00:20:54,240
I'm a fraud for exploiting Park Jae Sang,

248
00:20:55,068 --> 00:20:57,285
and you, who covered up that case

249
00:20:59,105 --> 00:21:02,373
to shield me, you're a fraud, too.

250
00:21:03,689 --> 00:21:05,460
Alright.

251
00:21:06,272 --> 00:21:08,747
If this is the price we're paying,

252
00:21:08,747 --> 00:21:10,139
let me fight it off.

253
00:21:10,139 --> 00:21:12,508
Between us and Park Jae Sang,

254
00:21:14,504 --> 00:21:17,347
either we or he

255
00:21:18,563 --> 00:21:21,146
has to die before this is over.

256
00:21:21,146 --> 00:21:25,563
So I'll shut him down, even if he has to die.

257
00:21:29,980 --> 00:21:31,979
I'll handle him on my end,

258
00:21:31,979 --> 00:21:34,939
you take care of things on your side.

259
00:21:34,939 --> 00:21:36,866
I'll call you back.

260
00:21:45,994 --> 00:21:48,078
Where are you?

261
00:21:48,078 --> 00:21:50,664
[Park Jae Sang]
Didn't I say to scrap the release?

262
00:21:50,664 --> 00:21:53,377
Those are the client's instructions!

263
00:21:56,171 --> 00:21:58,831
You'll get the agreed sum. Now where are you?

264
00:21:58,831 --> 00:22:00,759
[Live broadcast launches at 20:30]

265
00:22:00,759 --> 00:22:03,810
Money's meaningless to me now.

266
00:22:05,597 --> 00:22:09,190
Why do you all just exploit me
