398
00:36:08,899 --> 00:36:10,855
Gosh.

399
00:36:10,855 --> 00:36:14,765
It was eating me up so much

400
00:36:14,765 --> 00:36:17,685
I visited that fortune teller recently.

401
00:36:17,685 --> 00:36:19,959
I told you not to blow the allowance

402
00:36:19,959 --> 00:36:23,188
