413
00:36:49,689 --> 00:36:52,016
Don't try to brace yourself.

414
00:36:52,016 --> 00:36:54,772
Bend with it, or you'll snap.

415
00:36:54,772 --> 00:36:57,309
- Got it?
- Yeah, I got it.

416
