418
00:37:02,494 --> 00:37:07,248
Hold on, stay still. Get over here.

419
00:37:13,836 --> 00:37:16,505
You're at a pivotal moment right now.

420
00:37:16,505 --> 00:37:18,981
Looking too ragged isn't going to cut it,

421
00:37:18,981 --> 00:37:21,397
