528
00:46:43,938 --> 00:46:45,866
while the three clash formations

529
00:46:45,866 --> 00:46:47,034
[Son Guk Won]

530
00:46:47,034 --> 00:46:51,553
command military strength,
with the people's support,

531
00:46:51,553 --> 00:46:54,048
