Okay. I'll be in touch again.

536
00:47:22,155 --> 00:47:24,178
[Choi Ji Ho]

537
00:47:25,995 --> 00:47:27,535
It's me.

538
00:47:27,535 --> 00:47:28,635
Yes, Director.

539
00:47:28,635 --> 00:47:32,075
Didn't you say
we had bait stashed for a diversion?

540
00:47:32,075 --> 00:47:35,131
Right, there are a couple.
Where do you intend to deploy them?

541
00:47:37,501 --> 00:47:40,587
I'm looking to reel in Son Guk Won,

542
00:47:40,587 --> 00:47:44,219
but the mess he's made is just too massive.

543
00:47:44,219 --> 00:47:47,435
Do we have a plan that can match that level?

544
00:47:47,435 --> 00:47:51,306
Since his old scandals were already massive,
to pull this off...

545
00:47:51,306 --> 00:47:55,138
[Practice Room Logs, Unreleased Footage]
we'll need a long-game hot-cold approach.

546
00:47:55,138 --> 00:47:56,981
Plus, if this is election-grade,

547
00:47:56,981 --> 00:47:59,522
it'll require serious funding, right?

548
00:47:59,522 --> 00:48:01,521
Forget about the money.

549
00:48:01,521 --> 00:48:04,862
Prepare a tentpole scenario.

550
00:48:04,862 --> 00:48:07,274
[Breaking,
Bang and Chu Press Conference at 10 AM]

551
00:48:09,772 --> 00:48:11,076
Wait a second.

552
00:48:11,076 --> 00:48:12,358
[Breaking,
Bang and Chu Press Conference at 10 AM]

553
00:48:12,358 --> 00:48:14,689
This couple...

554
00:48:14,689 --> 00:48:17,674
they make for entertaining targets.

555
00:48:58,188 --> 00:49:00,638
Hello.

556
00:49:00,638 --> 00:49:03,303
I'm actress Chu Sang Ah.

557
00:49:04,647 --> 00:49:06,934
To begin,

558
00:49:06,934 --> 00:49:10,143
for Park Jae Sang, who is no longer with us,

559
00:49:12,638 --> 00:49:15,648
I offer my deepest condolences.

560
00:49:18,769 --> 00:49:20,730
Though the Oh Kwang Jae incident

561
00:49:20,730 --> 00:49:23,982
[Chu and Bang Couple, Urgent Press Conference]
left us beyond repair,

562
00:49:23,982 --> 00:49:25,992
at one time, he was

563
00:49:26,610 --> 00:49:29,704
someone I considered family.

564
00:49:30,522 --> 00:49:33,291
Following his release, I did all I could

565
00:49:34,105 --> 00:49:37,462
to restore my bond with Park Jae Sang,

566
00:49:40,835 --> 00:49:44,761
but consumed by rage and vengeance as he was,

567
00:49:45,397 --> 00:49:48,056
there was no getting through to him.

568
00:49:50,254 --> 00:49:52,852
As the situation grew worse,

569
00:49:53,689 --> 00:49:57,357
harm reached my family and my company,

570
00:49:58,981 --> 00:50:02,022
and despite my appeals of innocence,

571
00:50:02,022 --> 00:50:05,323
not a single person trusted my words.

572
00:50:06,522 --> 00:50:08,724
So even if it had to be this way,

573
00:50:10,463 --> 00:50:13,831
I wanted to prove I'm innocent.

574
00:50:17,022 --> 00:50:20,179
All that bad acting every single day,

575
00:50:20,179 --> 00:50:23,275
but that's Oscar-worthy, honestly.

576
00:50:23,275 --> 00:50:26,172
What happened to Park Jae Sang is tragic,

577
00:50:26,172 --> 00:50:29,680
[Chu and Bang Couple, Urgent Press Conference]
but I'm glad the misunderstanding

578
00:50:31,021 --> 00:50:33,454
is cleared at last.

579
00:50:33,454 --> 00:50:35,438
To all who stood

580
00:50:35,438 --> 00:50:39,185
by Bang Tae Seop and me through it all,

581
00:50:39,185 --> 00:50:41,859
I express my gratitude once more.

582
00:51:05,117 --> 00:51:08,128
After this case, we've been through

583
00:51:08,128 --> 00:51:12,132
endless suspicion and scrutiny,

584
00:51:12,132 --> 00:51:15,059
but I vow that we never commissioned a murder

585
00:51:15,884 --> 00:51:18,767
or concealed any wrongdoing.

586
00:51:18,767 --> 00:51:21,224
As a result, Chu Sang Ah endured

587
00:51:21,224 --> 00:51:24,912
devastating harm to her reputation

588
00:51:24,912 --> 00:51:27,725
and crippling financial losses, and I as well

589
00:51:27,725 --> 00:51:28,743
[Live Chat]

590
00:51:28,743 --> 00:51:31,855
was at risk of having

591
00:51:31,855 --> 00:51:33,737
my Changjo Party nomination revoked.

592
00:51:33,737 --> 00:51:36,493
[Always rooting for you from afar, Chu Sang Ah]
[Chu Sang Ah did nothing wrong]

593
00:51:36,493 --> 00:51:39,876
What gullible, pitiful idiots.

594
00:51:40,705 --> 00:51:43,212
Good morning!

595
00:51:44,188 --> 00:51:46,811
Oh, dear Mother.

596
00:51:46,811 --> 00:51:49,544
On the verge of losing it all,

597
00:51:49,544 --> 00:51:53,480
and the Bang couple just
knocked you down again.

598
00:51:53,480 --> 00:51:54,928
Hey!

599
00:51:54,928 --> 00:51:57,634
Don't bring a dog in here!

600
00:51:58,313 --> 00:52:00,476
My Petit here

601
00:52:00,476 --> 00:52:04,066
outranks you by bloodline.

602
00:52:06,815 --> 00:52:08,772
You're constantly getting beaten by those two,

603
00:52:08,772 --> 00:52:11,522
and still you babble about seizing WR.

604
00:52:11,522 --> 00:52:14,015
My nerves are shot right now,

605
00:52:14,015 --> 00:52:15,446
so close your mouth
and get out while I'm being polite.

606
00:52:15,446 --> 00:52:17,409
Hey.

607
00:52:20,049 --> 00:52:24,337
You're nothing but a stray
who latched on to mooch,

608
00:52:25,022 --> 00:52:26,881
while I'm

609
00:52:27,650 --> 00:52:32,011
the sole thoroughbred successor
of this household's bloodline.

610
00:52:33,258 --> 00:52:36,002
I'm not incapable of tearing you apart.

611
00:52:36,002 --> 00:52:38,638
I'm simply holding back.

612
00:52:38,638 --> 00:52:40,811
Aren't you going to get rid of this thing?

613
00:52:42,022 --> 00:52:43,223
Not "this thing." Petit.

614
00:52:43,223 --> 00:52:45,274
Shit.

615
00:52:47,105 --> 00:52:49,396
Even if you end up kicked to the curb,

616
00:52:49,396 --> 00:52:52,524
don't drag our family through the gutter.

617
00:52:52,524 --> 00:52:54,401
Come here. Goodbye, Mother.

618
00:52:54,401 --> 00:52:57,063
That son of a bitch...

619
00:52:57,063 --> 00:52:59,309
Not "son of a bitch." Petit.

620
00:52:59,309 --> 00:53:02,542
Get out. Get out!

621
00:53:10,814 --> 00:53:13,715
We were ruthlessly targeted and pursued.

622
00:53:13,715 --> 00:53:16,214
The people who persecuted us

623
00:53:16,214 --> 00:53:18,433
wielded their influence as a tool

624
00:53:18,433 --> 00:53:21,397
to prey on the weak for their own greed,

625
00:53:21,397 --> 00:53:23,188
manipulated the press,

626
00:53:23,188 --> 00:53:25,647
and even resorted to killing.

627
00:53:25,647 --> 00:53:28,401
Killing? What do you mean by that?

628
00:53:30,647 --> 00:53:33,855
What's he getting at now?

629
00:53:33,855 --> 00:53:35,929
Yet even with all their plotting,

630
00:53:35,929 --> 00:53:38,869
we refused to go over the edge.

631
00:53:40,272 --> 00:53:43,158
We're ready to fight once more.

632
00:53:43,158 --> 00:53:45,140
Citizens,

633
00:53:45,140 --> 00:53:48,423
I ask you to put your faith in us once more,

634
00:53:48,423 --> 00:53:50,689
and stand behind the fight

635
00:53:50,689 --> 00:53:53,084
we're about to carry forward.

636
00:53:53,084 --> 00:53:55,678
I humbly implore you.

637
00:54:05,016 --> 00:54:08,113
I'll put that tentpole plan
together personally.

638
00:54:08,113 --> 00:54:12,820
Glamorous, fierce, and sensational.

639
00:54:21,778 --> 00:54:24,319
Ms. Chu, any serious health concerns?

640
00:54:24,319 --> 00:54:26,139
What's the scale of the liabilities?

641
00:54:26,139 --> 00:54:27,839
What are your next steps from here?

642
00:54:27,839 --> 00:54:30,219
What drove Park Jae Sang
to end his life, in your view?

643
00:54:30,219 --> 00:54:32,624
- Chu Sang Ah!
- A comment, please!

644
00:54:32,624 --> 00:54:34,167
- Ms. Chu!
- A statement, please!

645
00:54:34,167 --> 00:54:35,063
Please, just one comment!

646
00:54:35,063 --> 00:54:36,920
- Did you have Park Jae Sang murdered?
- Ms. Chu.

647
00:54:36,920 --> 00:54:38,814
Ms. Chu!

648
00:54:38,814 --> 00:54:41,355
From the CCTV footage obtained on-site,

649
00:54:41,355 --> 00:54:44,761
we believe Park Jae Sang was killed by someone.

650
00:54:44,761 --> 00:54:46,012
The outside cameras show

651
00:54:46,012 --> 00:54:48,852
clear evidence of a woman entering,

652
00:54:48,852 --> 00:54:50,854
yet the interior CCTV in this building

653
00:54:50,854 --> 00:54:53,554
contains no trace of her.

654
00:54:53,554 --> 00:54:56,113
Somebody wiped the trail clean.

655
00:55:00,897 --> 00:55:03,245
Want me to kill him?

656
00:55:04,888 --> 00:55:06,666
Park Jae Sang.

657
00:55:07,855 --> 00:55:09,752
So?

658
00:55:11,981 --> 00:55:14,730
What is it you're curious about?

659
00:55:14,730 --> 00:55:16,710
You were close with Park Jae Sang,

660
00:55:16,710 --> 00:55:19,146
and you'd been seeing him

661
00:55:19,146 --> 00:55:21,161
up until recently.

662
00:55:21,161 --> 00:55:24,433
Does anyone come to mind?

663
00:55:28,022 --> 00:55:30,268
We have a scheduled appointment,

664
00:55:30,268 --> 00:55:32,075
so let's wrap this up.

665
00:55:39,814 --> 00:55:41,568
Did he not suggest suicide at the cafe?

666
00:55:41,568 --> 00:55:43,111
Are you dismissing the chance of foul play?

667
00:55:43,111 --> 00:55:44,939
Is there anyone you'd point to?

668
00:55:44,939 --> 00:55:46,159
- Just one comment, please.
- Ms. Chu.

669
00:55:46,159 --> 00:55:48,707
- Ms. Chu.
- Ms. Chu.

670
00:55:49,563 --> 00:55:51,377
Ms. Chu.

671
00:58:21,480 --> 00:58:23,605
The battle's already broken out.

672
00:58:23,605 --> 00:58:25,569
[Candidate No. 2 Bang Tae Seop]
It's not getting any easier.

673
00:58:25,569 --> 00:58:28,276
I must look like a fool to you.

674
00:58:28,276 --> 00:58:29,355
It's not that you need me.

675
00:58:29,355 --> 00:58:32,075
Now you'll die without me.

676
00:58:32,075 --> 00:58:35,631
What I can't possess, I'll shatter.

677
00:58:35,631 --> 00:58:37,291
I'll see this through to the very end.

678
00:58:37,291 --> 00:58:38,661
Put your faith and money in me,

679
00:58:38,661 --> 00:58:40,458
and there'll be no regrets.

680
00:58:40,458 --> 00:58:42,043
Chu Sang Ah.

681
00:58:42,043 --> 00:58:44,451
Can I borrow her for just one night?

682
00:58:44,451 --> 00:58:46,294
After coming this far,

683
00:58:46,294 --> 00:58:48,994
what's left but to break?
